LANGUAGE, MAINLY YIDDISH.

00:01:26.997 --> 00:01:29.797
SHALOM MR. ADALBERTO FRIED.

00:01:31.130 --> 00:01:34.641
mir fangen on mit aykh dem INTERVIEW,

00:01:34.997 --> 00:01:39.797
ikh volt aykh gebetn ir zolt undz dertseyln, koydem kol,

00:01:39.797 --> 00:01:43.286
ayer nomen, un shpeter vegn ayer familye, bite.

00:01:44.435 --> 00:01:49.147
mayn nomen iz Adalbert Frid, in yidish Avrom Borekh Frid.

00:01:50.003 --> 00:01:52.408
ikh bin geboyrn toyznt nayn hundert zibetsn,

00:01:52.614 --> 00:01:56.218
zibetsn detsember, tsufelik UNK hob ikh punkt haynt dem geburtstog.

00:01:56.698 --> 00:01:57.943
mazl tov.

00:02:00.519 --> 00:02:01.878
ikh,

00:02:02.428 --> 00:02:04.268
mayn tate hot geheysn Yosef,

00:02:04.422 --> 00:02:07.234
mayn mame hot geheysn Regina, Malek.

00:02:10.155 --> 00:02:13.319
mayn foter iz gevezn zeyer an inteligenter khsidisher yid,

00:02:13.413 --> 00:02:14.837
getrogn bord un peyes,

00:02:15.337 --> 00:02:17.823
a zeyer a balezener, inteligenter mentsh,

00:02:18.404 --> 00:02:22.252
⟨korespondirt⟩ un geredt perfekt daytsh un andere shprakhn,

00:02:24.038 --> 00:02:25.952
..

00:02:26.032 --> 00:02:29.904
hot gemakht parnose fun DIFFERENT BUSINESS, geven a BUSINESSMAN,

00:02:30.196 --> 00:02:34.732
gehat khemikaln fartretung fun Daytshland, er flegt forn a sakh keyn Daytshland.

00:02:36.632 --> 00:02:40.164
un, shpeter hobn mir gehat,

00:02:40.646 --> 00:02:44.097
shoyn in di ungarishe tsayt, hobn mir gehat a klenere veberay

00:02:44.104 --> 00:02:46.122
a TEX- TEXTILE fabrik.

00:02:45.447 --> 00:02:49.025
vegn dem vel mir nokh redn. ikh hob nor gevolt, ir zolt zayn azoy gut

00:02:49.025 --> 00:02:51.691
ir hot mir gezogt dem nomen fun ayer tatn?

00:02:51.691 --> 00:02:53.669
vos iz geshen mit ayer tatn?

00:02:53.532 --> 00:02:57.095
mayn tate iz deportirt gevorn yare fir un fertsik.

00:02:58.040 --> 00:03:02.585
tsuzamen mit mir un mit tsvey shvester mit a bruder.

00:03:02.858 --> 00:03:04.415
fun dem ze'mir dray aheymgekumen

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:04.548
un der foter iz nisht gekumen...

00:03:04.415 --> 00:03:06.478
fun dem ze'mir dray aheymgekumen,

00:03:06.478 --> 00:03:11.041
mayne tsvey shvester Etl un Rakhl, un ikh.

00:03:11.278 --> 00:03:15.017
ikh hob gehat a klenern bruder, er iz geven tsvey khadoshim far di bar mitsve,

00:03:15.458 --> 00:03:18.925
der iz leyder nisht aheymgekumen, Eli, Eli iz geven der nomen

00:03:19.774 --> 00:03:23.107
iz der foter mitn klenern bruder zenen nisht tsurikgekumen.

00:03:22.094 --> 00:03:23.615
nisht tsurikgekumen.

00:03:23.917 --> 00:03:25.469
vos iz geshen mit der muter?

00:03:25.370 --> 00:03:29.288
der muter iz geshtorbn yare nay-, nayn, yare fertsik.

00:03:30.135 --> 00:03:34.405
alt geven nayn un fertsik yor, fun BROST fun BREAST CANCER.

00:03:34.211 --> 00:03:36.156
vi hot geheysn di muter?

00:03:36.200 --> 00:03:43.328
 oyf yidish Sore Rivke, un nokh hot zi geheysn Regina, Regina Malek, Regina Frid

00:03:43.725 --> 00:03:46.014
ikh gedenk nisht tsi ir hot mir gezogt

00:03:46.014 --> 00:03:48.659
 fun van, vu zent ir geboyrn gevorn, velkhn plats?

00:03:48.236 --> 00:03:50.568
ikh bin geboyrn in NAGYKATA,

00:03:50.705 --> 00:03:55.266
mayn foter iz geven a soldat, di mame olehasholem iz gegangen bazukhn

00:03:55.670 --> 00:03:59.390
un in tsvishn hot zi gedarft geborn

00:04:00.111 --> 00:04:02.245
yetst zeyt azoy gut

00:04:02.245 --> 00:04:08.267
dertseylt mir vos ir gedenkt fun der heym, vi se hot zikh gelebt fa- biz di tsores hobn zikh ongehoybn.

00:04:08.555 --> 00:04:11.280
in der heym hobn mir gefirt a sheyn familye lebn.

00:04:11.355 --> 00:04:14.375
a khasidish yidish lebn.

00:04:14.431 --> 00:04:17.366
der tate fleg makhn sheyn parnose.

00:04:17.394 --> 00:04:20.673
m'iz gegangen koydem in shul, nokh dem UNK iz men gegangen in kheyder,

00:04:20.751 --> 00:04:22.397
shpeter iz men gegan in di yeshive,

00:04:22.609 --> 00:04:24.391
a por yor,

00:04:23.910 --> 00:04:25.828
in velkhe yeshive hot ir dort gelernt?

00:04:25.454 --> 00:04:28.675
in Dragomiresht un in Visheve.

00:04:28.676 --> 00:04:31.460
der tate iz geven a khosid fun a gevisn rebn?

00:04:30.932 --> 00:04:33.364
fun Antonir un Vizhnits.

00:04:36.578 --> 00:04:40.814
er tate fleg mikh a sakh mol mitnemen, der vizhnitser iz geven alter vizhnitser in Grosvardayn.

00:04:41.060 --> 00:04:44.110
dos iz geven nisht vayt, tsvey hundert kilometer fun SATU MARE.

00:04:45.340 --> 00:04:48.828
flegt er mikh merere mol mitnemen fun rebn olev- zikhroyne-livrokhe.

00:04:53.721 --> 00:04:58.997
azoy iz dos gegangen biz yare nayn un draysik,

00:04:59.633 --> 00:05:01.362
ikh hob gedarft aynrukn,

00:05:02.091 --> 00:05:06.258
di balebatishere yingelekh flegn geyn nisht far tsvey yor,

00:05:06.731 --> 00:05:09.922
me fleg nemen a ferd, me fleg koyfn an eygn ferd,

00:05:10.248 --> 00:05:13.591
un me fleg geyn, me fl- me fleg es onrufn oyf rumenish SKIMBAZH,

00:05:13.909 --> 00:05:18.058
dos heyst der ferd iz geven mayn, ikh hob es gedarft arayngebn farn militer,

00:05:19.927 --> 00:05:22.893
se hot gekost finef un tsvantsik, draysik toyznt daler aza ferd,

00:05:23.579 --> 00:05:24.821
un eygene kleyder,

00:05:24.870 --> 00:05:27.775
me ho'mir gehat sheyne kleyder, me ho- me ho'mir oysgekukt vi ofitsirn,

00:05:27.920 --> 00:05:29.796
eygene shtivl, eygene dos,

00:05:29.922 --> 00:05:34.300
un di UNK hobn mir gehat in di shtot.

00:05:35.028 --> 00:05:36.534
flegn mir aheymgeyn,

00:05:36.922 --> 00:05:39.394
flegn mir ahingeyn gants fri, im zekse,

00:05:39.634 --> 00:05:42.449
un fleg mir nokh mitog, im fineve, im zekse aheymkumen.

00:05:43.743 --> 00:05:47.650
flegn mir mitnemen kost fun der heym, me ho'mir gegesn nor koshers ho'mir gegesn.

00:05:49.259 --> 00:05:52.037
normal hot men gedarft dinen dray khadoshim.

00:05:52.773 --> 00:05:57.452
ober azoy vi s'iz geven nayn un draysik, s'iz arayngegangen in fertsik, hot zikh gemakht, ongehoybn di krig shoyn,

00:05:59.850 --> 00:06:02.191
Rusnland hot bazetst dem Tshernovits,

00:06:02.542 --> 00:06:05.304
hobn mir gehat a OBERLEUTNANT,

00:06:05.768 --> 00:06:11.187
UNK, er fleg nisht veln nemen gelt, ober er fleg nemen gelt oyf an andern oyfn.

00:06:11.625 --> 00:06:17.227
er fleg zogn er nemt nisht keyn gelt ober er vil koyfn hober far di ferd.

00:06:18.199 --> 00:06:23.580
fleg mir hobn eynem vos er fleg farkoyfn, eyner Leyvi, vos er fleg farkoyfn hober,

00:06:23.814 --> 00:06:25.851
fleg mir bay dem Leyvi ayntsoln,

00:06:26.274 --> 00:06:29.413
bateyln oyf yedn khoydesh a toyznt tsu fuftsn hundert lay,

00:06:29.877 --> 00:06:33.090
un er fleg es shoyn nokh dem oyfnemen in gelt.

00:06:33.199 --> 00:06:36.679
ze'mir geven azoy, ikh veys nisht, tsvelef, fuftsn yinglekh.

00:06:36.999 --> 00:06:38.957
er fleg makhn sheyn gelt lebn undz.

00:06:39.368 --> 00:06:44.800
er hot zikh take gants anshtendik banemen b- mit undz, azoy bay di instruktsye, un in algemeyn,

00:06:45.951 --> 00:06:50.174
shpeter, ven di rusn hobn bazetst Tshernovits,

00:06:50.411 --> 00:06:54.463
hot er undz tsamgerufn, di yidishe SKIMBAZHN, s'iz geven a por goyim oykh tsvishn

00:06:55.639 --> 00:06:57.057
zogt er, "her tsu,"

00:06:57.322 --> 00:06:58.483
zogt er, "biz hitst

00:06:58.559 --> 00:07:01.552
bin ikh geven, bin ikh in geshtanen tsu farfign,

00:07:01.833 --> 00:07:04.419
ikh hob enk ales nokhgegebn, ir hot gedarft a mol urloyb,

00:07:06.589 --> 00:07:09.789
ober fun haynt on hob ikh mikh geendert in gantsn," zogt er,

00:07:10.814 --> 00:07:14.062
m'iz geven zeyer iberrasht, vos iz geshen?

00:07:14.574 --> 00:07:16.209
zogt er, "her tsu," zogt er,

00:07:16.611 --> 00:07:21.041
in Tshernovits hobn di rusn bazetst Rumenyen.

00:07:21.227 --> 00:07:23.154
Tshernovits iz geven a Rumenishe shtot.

00:07:24.154 --> 00:07:26.348
un vi ikh bin informirt, me hot undz informirt

00:07:26.418 --> 00:07:30.578
az di yidn zenen aroysgegangen mit seyfer toyres vartn di rusn,

00:07:30.674 --> 00:07:34.637
un me hot geharget un geshlogn rumenishe soldatn un rumenishe ofitsirn."

00:07:35.395 --> 00:07:38.012
zogt er, "az ir yidn zent umshtand geven oyf azoy vos,"

00:07:38.143 --> 00:07:40.468
zogt er, "vil ikh mer nisht visn keyn yidishn UNK.

00:07:40.887 --> 00:07:44.341
ir zolt nisht vartn keyn urloyb, keyn frayheyt fun mir,

00:07:44.542 --> 00:07:46.019
ikh hob mikh in gantsn geendert."

00:07:47.493 --> 00:07:52.299
shpeter ho'mir ho'mir prubirt im tsu gebn tsu farshteyn az s'iz nisht in gantsn azoy geven,

00:07:52.428 --> 00:07:56.708
di yidn hobn nisht keyn teyl genumen in di vi, m'iz nisht gegangen mit keyn seyfer toyres,

00:07:56.826 --> 00:08:00.927
s'iz do a por komunistn dos ba- balangt nisht, dos heyst nisht dos gantse yidntum.

00:08:01.027 --> 00:08:04.781
nu, s'iz do yedn, afi- afile in UNK iz do farshidene diferentser.

00:08:05.575 --> 00:08:08.495
shpeter hot er zikh baruikt undz ze'mir tsurik gevorn gute brider.

00:08:10.197 --> 00:08:13.352
biz vi lang hot ir gedint in militer?

00:08:14.983 --> 00:08:17.371
shpeter, nokh finef khadoshim,

00:08:17.658 --> 00:08:20.047
hobn mir shoyn gedarft nokh tsvey khadoshim fray vern,

00:08:20.664 --> 00:08:25.005
hot men undz ibergeshtelt undzer regiment keyn Kloyznburg. Kloyznburg.

00:08:26.182 --> 00:08:28.575
dos iz a dray hundert kilometer fun Satmer.

00:08:29.346 --> 00:08:33.515
dos iz eyn un draysiker, azoy hob ikh gedint befor bay di tsvey un draysiker artilerye,

00:08:33.879 --> 00:08:38.124
me hot undz ibergeshtelt tsu di eyn un draysiker artilerye, keyn Kloyznburg.

00:08:40.094 --> 00:08:42.233
befor ikh bin avekgeforn,

00:08:42.719 --> 00:08:46.440
iz di mame olehasholem zeyer krank geven, shoyn demolts geven

00:08:47.118 --> 00:08:51.587
in di letste vokhn fun funem fun ir krankeyt nebekh, me hot nor demolts keyn, keyn

00:08:51.700 --> 00:08:56.916
CANCER, brust CANCER, me hot nisht gevust vos dos iz. s'iz geven a profesor in Kloyznburg eyner, dokter Royt,

00:08:57.872 --> 00:08:59.311
er hot zi operirt,

00:08:59.462 --> 00:09:01.824
voltst gevolt UNK shmertsn gehat.

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:04.358
nisht geven tsum oyshaltn. flegn kumen yedn tog

00:09:04.624 --> 00:09:07.381
tsu fray fir doktoyrim, me hot ir, me hot nisht ge-

00:09:07.488 --> 00:09:10.745
geshoynt keyn gelt, me hot gehaltn UNK yedn tog.

00:09:12.268 --> 00:09:16.526
zi hot shoyn nebekh nisht gekent geyn, me fleg geyn mit a shtekn dort in shtub a por shpan,

00:09:18.154 --> 00:09:19.734
ven ikh bin aroysgegangen

00:09:21.058 --> 00:09:25.262
hot zi mikh bagleyt biz tsu di tir, zeyer geveynt, ikh zi gekusht, zogt zi, "kind zis,

00:09:25.330 --> 00:09:28.034
zolst nisht fargesn tsu geyn davenen yedn tog.

00:09:28.907 --> 00:09:32.410
ikh fleg davenen yedn tog, in der heym, a sakh mol in shul,

00:09:32.479 --> 00:09:35.379
ober ongezogt mir deys, ikh zol nisht fargesn tsu geyn davenen,

00:09:35.439 --> 00:09:38.383
zi hot mir gevolt tsu zogn ikh zol nisht fargesn kadesh tsu zogn yedn tog.

00:09:40.310 --> 00:09:43.492
me darf nisht bamerkn vosere situatsye ikh bin avekgeforn,

00:09:43.853 --> 00:09:46.000
ikh hob mikh demolts, ikh hob nokh demolts nisht gereykhert.

00:09:46.141 --> 00:09:48.136
ikh hob mikh demolts genumen reykhern.

00:09:48.969 --> 00:09:52.220
un ikh fleg ontsindn un oysleshn di tsigaretlekh.

00:09:52.780 --> 00:09:56.541
ikh hob gehat a por khaveyrim fun kindvayz, ze'mir geven fun der heym khaveyrim,

00:09:56.646 --> 00:09:59.096
dernokh geven in eynem soldatn mit mir,

00:09:59.229 --> 00:10:03.429
zey hobn mikh prubirt tsu baruikn ales, ober se hot dokh nisht geholfn.

00:10:09.375 --> 00:10:12.205
ikh bin alts geganen, ikh hob gehat a FIRST COUSIN,

00:10:12.303 --> 00:10:17.900
eynem Yisroel Dovid Frid, er lebt shoyn nebekh nisht, er iz geshtorbn far a dray, fir yor do in Yisroel, er hot do gevoynt letst.

00:10:19.082 --> 00:10:23.798
fleg ikh tsun im geyn alts fregn tsi me hot nisht telefonirt ikh hob mikh nisht getroyt zeyer tsu rufn oykh nisht aheym,

00:10:24.881 --> 00:10:26.715
zogt er neyn er veys nisht gornisht.

00:10:27.123 --> 00:10:31.273
er hot yo gevust vayl me hot telefonirt, un me hot gedost, ober far mir hot er gezogt er veyst nisht gornisht.

00:10:33.716 --> 00:10:38.031
di mame olehasholem iz, tsen tog deroyf geshtorbn.

00:10:38.583 --> 00:10:40.609
bay mir, mir hot men nisht gevolt dertseyln.

00:10:40.699 --> 00:10:43.224
di khaveyrim, me hot yeder gevust nor ikh hob nisht gevust.

00:10:44.478 --> 00:10:46.730
me hot gevolt se zol durkhgeyn di shloyshim,

00:10:46.852 --> 00:10:49.266
ikh zol nisht darfn zitsn keyn akht tog shive.

00:10:52.055 --> 00:10:55.903
endlekh, nokh s'iz durkh di shloyshim,

00:10:57.358 --> 00:11:00.280
zogt mir a khaver, zogt er,

00:11:01.488 --> 00:11:04.110
"her tsu," zogt er, "du darfst zogn kadesh."

00:11:06.862 --> 00:11:13.636
ikh hob gekhalesht, ikh bin tsamgefaln dortn. me hot mikh koym dermuntert dort,

00:11:13.636 --> 00:11:20.084
ikh hob gefregt ven dos iz geshen, zogn zey s'iz shoyn geshen nokh far tsvey a halb vokhn, men hot mir nor nisht gevolt demolts oyszogn.

00:11:20.727 --> 00:11:22.838
ikh zol nisht darfn zitsn ven ikh bin in militer.

00:11:23.271 --> 00:11:26.025
"mir ho'mir prubirt," zogt er, "tsu erleydikn baym mayor,

00:11:26.339 --> 00:11:27.849
baym komendant,

00:11:28.332 --> 00:11:30.595
zolst kenen aheymforn oyf di levaye,

00:11:30.862 --> 00:11:33.213
me hot gehaltn tsurik di levaye mit a tog,

00:11:33.273 --> 00:11:37.053
mir ho'mir ales prubirt ontsuvendn, me hot tsugezogt tsen toyznt lay, a sakh gelt geven,

00:11:37.421 --> 00:11:41.837
un beshum-oyfn, me hot es nisht gekent demolts avek, avekgeyn avek forn aheym, undz ho'mir ales prubirt."

00:11:47.341 --> 00:11:55.917
endlekh, fleg ikh kumen shabes fleg ikh esn bay mayn COUSIN bay dem Sroel Dovid Frid,

00:11:56.612 --> 00:12:00.810
shoyn me hot shoyn efsher oykh gevust, UNK oykh leyder gevust befor shin alef,

00:12:01.918 --> 00:12:04.064
iz durkhgegan nokh a por vokhn,

00:12:06.431 --> 00:12:09.321
in total hobn mir gedint a nayn khadoshim, hobn mir gedint,

00:12:09.623 --> 00:12:10.884
⟨INSTEAD⟩ dray,

00:12:11.837 --> 00:12:13.264
un ikh bin aheymgekumen.

00:12:13.467 --> 00:12:14.585
bafrayt gevorn.

00:12:14.534 --> 00:12:15.539
bafrayt gevorn.

00:12:15.457 --> 00:12:16.566
ven iz dos geven?

00:12:16.432 --> 00:12:18.153
s'iz geven yare fertsik.

00:12:19.738 --> 00:12:22.147
mit ayer erloybenish volt ikh nokh gevolt

00:12:22.147 --> 00:12:24.836
etlekhe kurtse fragn fun frier.

00:12:24.836 --> 00:12:28.036
lebndik in SATU MARE, hot ir gelebt dort?

00:12:27.228 --> 00:12:27.945
yo.

00:12:28.036 --> 00:12:33.107
lebndik in SATU MARE, s'iz geven a groyse yidishe shtot, se hot geven a sakh yidn.

00:12:32.790 --> 00:12:34.149
fuftsn toyznt yidn

00:12:34.111 --> 00:12:39.378
s'iz dort geven bay aykh oykh, ir zent geven, hot ir mir gezogt, a khasidishe, ortodoksishe familye.

00:12:40.685 --> 00:12:43.901
s'iz dort geven bay aykh oykh tsienistishe tetikeyt in shtot

00:12:43.901 --> 00:12:46.842
un zent ir geven epes farbindn mit dem.

00:12:44.813 --> 00:12:51.372
neyn ikh bin nisht geven ober ikh hob gehat, a COUSIN hob ikh gehat vos iz geven a groyser tsienist a groyser mizrekhist, er flegt, gegangen oyf HACHSHARA,

00:12:51.776 --> 00:12:56.486
yo, ikh hob gehat in di familye, ikh hob gehat a SECOND COUSIN, dem tatns a COUSIN, a froy,

00:12:56.553 --> 00:12:58.999
er lebt nokh hitst, er iz shoyn alt bald bay di nayntsik,

00:12:59.250 --> 00:13:02.364
aroysgekumen in di yare zibn un tsvantsik, akht un tsvantsik keyn Yisroel.

00:13:02.391 --> 00:13:05.792
zey voynen in Yerusholaim, der man lebt oykh nokh,

00:13:05.793 --> 00:13:07.832
zi hot gearbet in a shpitol, hot zi gearbet,

00:13:07.968 --> 00:13:10.790
hot ir gevust vegn tsienistishe...

00:13:08.868 --> 00:13:10.669
UNK me hot gevust, yo! yo.

00:13:10.790 --> 00:13:13.324
ober ir aleyn zent ir nisht geven farmisht.

00:13:11.987 --> 00:13:13.202
ikh bin nisht, neyn, ikh bin...

00:13:13.202 --> 00:13:14.975
ikh bin kholile nisht geven anti-tsienist.

00:13:16.136 --> 00:13:20.025
yetst lebndik dortn far di mil- far di rumenishe tsaytn,

00:13:20.025 --> 00:13:23.025
far, nokh far ir zent arayn in militer,

00:13:23.358 --> 00:13:27.714
hot men gefilt epes antisemitishkeyt far di rumenishe tsaytn?

00:13:28.495 --> 00:13:31.753
antisemitish- antisemitishkeyt hot men gefilt shtendik.

00:13:32.166 --> 00:13:37.224
shkotsim, ze'mir geven kleyne kinder mir flegn mir geyn in kheyder arayn, ikh bin aheymkumen oyf der nakht, flegt men undz opvartn,

00:13:37.307 --> 00:13:38.932
men flegt undz raysn di peyes,

00:13:39.048 --> 00:13:41.881
flegn undz varfn shteyner, s'iz tomed azoy geven.

00:13:41.965 --> 00:13:44.449
Rumenye iz geven an antisemitishe medine.

00:13:44.721 --> 00:13:47.790
nor eyn UNK hot es gehat fun di Unger- Ungarn,

00:13:47.916 --> 00:13:50.007
az di rumener hobn genumen gelt.

00:13:50.702 --> 00:13:52.874
in far gelt hot men gekent ales erleydikn.

00:13:53.185 --> 00:13:55.217
vos bay di ungarn hot men nisht gekent.

00:13:55.564 --> 00:13:57.229
deys iz geven der diferents.

00:13:57.756 --> 00:14:01.749
un zey zenen geven efsher farbisene, di ungarn zenen geven farbisenere antisemitn.

00:14:02.101 --> 00:14:07.626
mir hobn gezen tsu ende az der, Ungarn hot aroysgegebn a halb milyon yidn, un der rumener hot nisht aroysgegebn.

00:14:07.750 --> 00:14:11.431
me hot gehat dey DIFFERENT lagers vos zenen geshtorbn hunderter toyznter yidn.

00:14:11.641 --> 00:14:14.789
un un DIFFERENT UNK farshidene dos

00:14:14.854 --> 00:14:17.330
ober s'iz dokh nisht geven, zey hobn geshokhtn yidn,

00:14:17.396 --> 00:14:23.576
un me hot aroysgeshtelt in di fleysh benk az dos iz CARNE kosher, koshere fleysh.

00:14:23.576 --> 00:14:30.006
geshokhtn merere yi- merere mol yidn vi di ⟨ayzngarder⟩,

00:14:31.190 --> 00:14:33.879
ober s'iz dokh nisht geven

00:14:32.346 --> 00:14:35.387
UNK a bisl andersh vi do.

00:14:34.074 --> 00:14:35.825
andersh vi bay di vi bay di bay di Ungarn

00:14:36.331 --> 00:14:40.027
yo. zent ir in nayntsn fertsik tsurikgekumen aheym, UNK...

00:14:39.321 --> 00:14:40.902
bin ikh tsurikkumen aheym

00:14:43.628 --> 00:14:50.216
un ikh hob gehat a fabrikl vos iz geven, ikh hob gemakht azelkhe

00:14:50.902 --> 00:14:54.494
 atores vos iz oyf di taleysim.

00:14:54.813 --> 00:15:00.271
s'iz geven dort a poylishe arbet, fun azelkhe hoyz, di di hent arbet,

00:15:00.587 --> 00:15:03.316
ikh hob gehat a fabrikl, ikh hob gehat, mit tsvelef, fuftsn shikslekh,

00:15:03.399 --> 00:15:07.684
ikh hob nisht gehat keyn yidishe meydlekh vayl ikh hob nisht gevolt men zol oyslernen dos fakh, vayl ikh hob es gelernt fun poyln,

00:15:07.818 --> 00:15:11.995
ikh bin geven der eyntsiker vos ikh hob es gemakht in gants Rumenyen un shpeter in gants Ungarn.

00:15:12.668 --> 00:15:15.042
un ikh hob fardint aleyn gelt,

00:15:15.469 --> 00:15:18.252
geven b- b- BUSY ikh bin geven farnumen.

00:15:20.116 --> 00:15:28.874
un in yare tsvey un fertsik hobn undz bazetst di Ungarn.

00:15:29.307 --> 00:15:32.809
in Ungarn iz shoyn geven a yidish gezets, kegn yidn,

00:15:33.785 --> 00:15:38.264
az a yid ken nisht hobn aleyn keyn eygene BUSINESS oyf zayn nomen,

00:15:39.420 --> 00:15:42.172
un nisht keyn fabrik, un nisht keyn gesheft,

00:15:43.589 --> 00:15:46.079
undz hobn mir gehat di tate mame ho'mir gehat beshutfes

00:15:46.495 --> 00:15:50.114
a a veberay, an ar-

00:15:50.342 --> 00:15:53.373
TEXTILE fabrik, es hobn gearbet fertsik fuftsik mentshn dort.

00:15:55.794 --> 00:15:57.293
hot er oykh gemuzt hobn

00:15:57.639 --> 00:16:02.212
a goyishn nomen, er hot gehat a nomen eyner KEREKESH, KEREKESH SHANDOR.

00:16:02.301 --> 00:16:05.291
vos me hot im getsolt a por toyznt PENGE a khoydesh,

00:16:05.462 --> 00:16:08.351
ungarish gelt, er zol gebn dem nomen.

00:16:08.459 --> 00:16:10.294
shtroyman hot men dos gerufn.

00:16:11.425 --> 00:16:13.723
s'iz geven, oyf zayn nomen iz geven di firme,

00:16:13.806 --> 00:16:16.218
un di eygntimer zenen geven tsvey yidn.

00:16:18.699 --> 00:16:23.134
un me hot oysge- oysgetrakht farshidene tsores shoyn far yidn demolts, demolts hot zikh shoyn ongehoybn...

00:16:23.607 --> 00:16:26.473
vos far a gzeyres gedenkt ir fun yene tsaytn?

00:16:26.757 --> 00:16:29.262
farshidene gezetsn, ikh veys UNK

00:16:29.882 --> 00:16:35.254
gezetsn az UNK, a yid, a yid hot nisht getort hobn tsu ton mit keyn goyishe shikse, ikh meyn

00:16:36.001 --> 00:16:39.511
 farshidene and- andere zakhn.

00:16:39.543 --> 00:16:42.094
UNK ir darft shoyn trogn epes a simen?

00:16:40.706 --> 00:16:43.164
nokh nisht, nokh nisht, ikh halt nokh nisht derbay,

00:16:43.209 --> 00:16:47.574
ikh halt nokh nisht derbay.

00:16:47.613 --> 00:16:53.201
in yare tsvey un fertsik ze'mir bafrayt gevorn, dos heyst bafrayt gevorn,

00:16:53.810 --> 00:16:58.656
v- di ungarn, me hot gepasknt demolts, Daytshland az Transilvenyen

00:16:58.767 --> 00:17:01.477
darf men tsurikgebn a teyl far di Ungarn.

00:17:02.721 --> 00:17:06.482
iz dos geven arayngerekhnt Satmer un Grosvardayn un Kloyznburg,

00:17:10.270 --> 00:17:14.342
un fun di Karpatn-Rus hobn zey oykh tsugenumen,

00:17:14.342 --> 00:17:17.643
Karpaten-Rus. dos iz oykh geven a mol Ungarn.

00:17:23.114 --> 00:17:29.041
un demolts hot zikh ongehoybn groyse antisemitizm, di ungern zenen geven gresere antisemitn nokh vi di, vi di rumener.

00:17:30.050 --> 00:17:32.460
un yidn hobn keyn shum rekhtn nisht gehat.

00:17:38.004 --> 00:17:44.062
ikh muz m- do makhn a shtikl parentez, vayl s- shpeter vet tsu nits kumen, ikh vel nokh redn iber dem.

00:17:44.907 --> 00:17:47.777
di ungarn zenen arayngekumen a por khadoshim deroyf,

00:17:47.906 --> 00:17:50.329
ikh bin per tsufal geven in der heym

00:17:51.653 --> 00:17:53.970
mit di shvester, s'iz geven a fraytik mitog,

00:17:53.970 --> 00:17:59.472
iz gekumen tsvey politsey un zey zukhn JOSZEF Frid.

00:18:00.788 --> 00:18:05.605
der tate iz geven a tsiviler mentsh, nisht gehat keyn, mit keynem tsu ton. a korekter mentsh.

00:18:07.188 --> 00:18:09.868
"vos vilstu der fun JOSZEF Frid?" freg ikh im.

00:18:10.505 --> 00:18:16.566
zogt er der komendant fun di politsey hot mir gezogt ikh zol ahi- ahinshteln JOSZEF Frid, me darf im hobn.

00:18:20.793 --> 00:18:26.604
bin ikh tsugegangen tsun a firme vos ikh hob gevust di tate gefint zikh dort, ikh hob dort getrofn dem tate, olevasholem.

00:18:27.783 --> 00:18:29.537
er hot zikh oykh zeyer dershrokn,

00:18:29.735 --> 00:18:32.629
politsey, me hot gevust az di antisemitishe politsey,

00:18:32.629 --> 00:18:35.307
UNK etlekhe zeyer groyse antisemitn geven.

00:18:36.757 --> 00:18:39.181
hobn mir gehat dort, antkegn di politsey iz geven der post.

00:18:39.559 --> 00:18:41.684
dort iz geven varem, s'iz geven vinter,

00:18:43.429 --> 00:18:45.815
feber, tsi velkher khoydesh iz es geven.

00:18:47.273 --> 00:18:48.462
zogt der tate,

00:18:48.523 --> 00:18:50.995
"vart do on bay di post, un vest zen

00:18:51.056 --> 00:18:54.607
az biz a halbe sho ikh kum nisht aroys, zolstu visn az me hot mikh arestirt."

00:18:56.879 --> 00:19:00.093
ikh vart a halbe sho, dray fertl sho, s'iz geven fraytik nokh mitog,

00:19:00.837 --> 00:19:05.610
nokh anderthalbn sho, endlekh der tate rukt zikh aroys, un ikh bin gegangen antkegn

00:19:06.299 --> 00:19:09.934
un shmeykhlt, zogt er, "kenst zikh nisht forshteln far vos me hot mikh gerufn."

00:19:12.099 --> 00:19:17.414
zogt er, "undz hobn mir gevoynt a mol in a in a, ikh veys far tsvontsik yor, far etlekhe tsvontsik yor,

00:19:17.509 --> 00:19:18.950
di DRINYE gas.

00:19:20.031 --> 00:19:23.666
dort iz geven der hoyz her iz geven eyner SEGENYI.

00:19:24.734 --> 00:19:27.661
dem zun, der heyst SEGENYI KAROL,

00:19:27.758 --> 00:19:29.971
der iz der politsey shef haynt do.

00:19:31.067 --> 00:19:34.600
er hot nokh gekukt dem aynmeldungs, dos KARTOTEK,

00:19:35.111 --> 00:19:39.565
hot er gevolt zen, der iz antlofn yene tsayt fun Rumenyen

00:19:39.650 --> 00:19:43.243
keyn Ungarn, er zol nisht dinen in mil- in rumenisher militer.

00:19:43.640 --> 00:19:47.533
er iz durkhgegan an ofitsir shul, biz vi lang er iz gevorn, kolonel iz er gevorn,

00:19:47.956 --> 00:19:52.163
un iz er gevorn bay di politsey der shef fun di satmere politsey.

00:19:56.830 --> 00:19:59.978
ven di tate iz arayngekumen, hot er zofort gefregt, "du bist,

00:20:00.054 --> 00:20:02.951
Frid JOSZEF," ungarish, zogt er, "yo."

00:20:03.421 --> 00:20:06.604
zogt er, "her tsu, ikh veys nisht tsi du gedenkst nokh oyf mir tsi neyn,"

00:20:07.319 --> 00:20:11.185
zogt er, "ikh bin SEGENYI KAROL," zogt er, "haynt bin ikh der shef fun di politsey,"

00:20:11.462 --> 00:20:14.729
zogt er, "darfst dikh gornisht shrekn, zets dikh arop in a fotel dort,"

00:20:14.840 --> 00:20:16.577
zogt er, "ikh hob nokh gekukt

00:20:18.120 --> 00:20:22.080
tsi, in UNK tsi tsi du ekzistirst nokh,

00:20:22.159 --> 00:20:24.378
JOSZEF Frid tsi er ekzistirt, hob ikh getrofn yo.

00:20:24.563 --> 00:20:26.077
un ikh hob getrofn vu du voynst.

00:20:26.782 --> 00:20:29.207
SO, ikh hob dikh bashtelt far dem," zogt er, "nokh

00:20:29.323 --> 00:20:31.130
finef un tsvontsik yor," zogt er,

00:20:31.304 --> 00:20:34.777
"vil ikh dikh zen, ikh gedenk undz ho'mir zeyer gut gelebt," zogt er, "mit di eltern.

00:20:36.720 --> 00:20:39.437
di UNK gebayde iz geven an ant- an antisemitishe mishpokhe.

00:20:40.081 --> 00:20:42.150
un er aleyn vorshaynlekh iz oykh geven an antisemit.

00:20:42.826 --> 00:20:46.056
ober azoy vi yeder antisemit un yeder porets hot zikh zayn yid,

00:20:46.519 --> 00:20:50.558
zogt er, "her mikh tsu," zogt er, "du vest zayn mayn hoyz-yid," azoy zogt, "er ikh vel epes darfn,"

00:20:51.091 --> 00:20:58.622
zogt er, "vel ikh nokh dir bafeln," zogt er, "un ikh vil zolst yedn khoydesh tsu mir tsukumen," zogt er, "ikh vil mikh iber farshidene zakhn shoyel-eytse zayn mit dir.

00:20:59.486 --> 00:21:01.058
s'iz take azoy geven.

00:21:01.357 --> 00:21:04.588
der tate hot zikh mit im zeyer shtark bafrayndet, er fleg im shikn

00:21:04.651 --> 00:21:07.650
vayn, n- oyf ma-, oyf peysekh matses,

00:21:07.811 --> 00:21:11.831
nisht vayl er hot es gedarft ober, far oyfmerkzamkeyt.

00:21:14.412 --> 00:21:18.171
ikh hob es far dem dertseylt vayl ikh vel shpeter tsukumen nokh tsu dem.

00:21:22.294 --> 00:21:29.640
ze'mir, tsvey un fertsik, s'iz geven anfang AUGUST,

00:21:29.739 --> 00:21:31.797
iz oysgekumen demolts tishebov.

00:21:33.088 --> 00:21:39.479
bin ikh gekumen mit mayn got-zelikn foter in shul arayn, un den, s'iz geven aza kloyz hobn gedavnt dort a hundert hundert tsvontsik mentshn dort,

00:21:40.042 --> 00:21:42.420
undz hobn mir gevoynt a bisl vayt fun der shul,

00:21:46.439 --> 00:21:48.016
ikh kum in shul arayn,

00:21:48.107 --> 00:21:52.539
ze ikh, der oylem kukt azoy oyf mir, azoy farshidn yeder eyner,

00:21:53.112 --> 00:21:56.489
bald heybt zikh eyner oyf me hot gehaltn in mitn davenen shoyn, zogt er,

00:21:57.014 --> 00:22:02.229
tishebov zitst men dokh azoy oyf der erd, dort oyf azelkhe kleyne benk, dort niderike benklekh,

00:22:03.465 --> 00:22:06.588
zogt er mir, "du host nisht bakumen?"

00:22:07.102 --> 00:22:08.282
freg ikh im, "vos?"

00:22:10.903 --> 00:22:14.097
zogt er, "dey nakht hot men oysgeteylt aynruf tsetl,

00:22:14.331 --> 00:22:15.970
