00:22:17.025 --> 00:22:22.486
zogt er, " oyb du host nisht bakumen biz aher," zogt er, "biz in der fri, biz hitst," zogt er, "vayl me hot nekhtn nakht shoyn aroysgetrogn," zogt er, "farn oylem."

00:22:22.724 --> 00:22:26.326
geven dort dray, fir yinglekh oykh, fun besmedresh, vos hobn bakumen aynruf tsetl.

00:22:29.232 --> 00:22:33.540
ikh muz do makhn a shtikl parentez, az mit fir vokhn befor,

00:22:33.920 --> 00:22:39.309
hot men oykh ayngerufn, a tsvey hundert yinglekh, tsvey hundert, tsvey hundert tsen yinglekh, fun Satmer.

00:22:39.823 --> 00:22:44.105
mir zenen mir shpeter, tsvey vokhn, tsi dray vokhn deroyf, gevoyr gevorn,

00:22:44.390 --> 00:22:48.056
az me hot di khevre, dem oylem aroysgefirt keyn Rusland.

00:22:48.498 --> 00:22:53.797
zey zoln oyfheybn di UNK dos, vos zenen nebekh... keyn finef protsent nisht tsurikgekumen fun zey.

00:22:56.447 --> 00:23:02.712
azoy ze'mir zeyer dershrokn geven, mir ho'mir bashlosn az, me ho'mir moyre gehat az undz vel mir oykh, me vet undz oykh aroysfirn keyn Rusland,

00:23:02.805 --> 00:23:05.733
mir ho'mir gevust Rusland iz der toyt. dos iz toyt.

00:23:10.816 --> 00:23:14.180
ikh hob opgezogt di kines dort in besmedresh dort, a tsvey sho dort geven,

00:23:14.678 --> 00:23:17.815
ikh hob nokh alts moyre gehat tsu, ikh bin aheymgekumen

00:23:18.221 --> 00:23:23.724
freg ikh vider di shvester, me ho'mir gehat a dinst dort, zogt zi "neyn, borekhashem..."

00:23:26.265 --> 00:23:30.747
s'iz durkhgegangen, s'iz shoyn geven mitog tsayt, eyns tsvey a zeyger, zogt mir der tate,

00:23:31.057 --> 00:23:33.817
"host nisht bakumen biz hitst ikh bin zikher du vest nisht bakumen."

00:23:37.039 --> 00:23:41.613
endlekh far nakhts, shoyn geven azoy finef zeks nokh mitog, rukt zikh on, mit undz baym toyer hobn mir hobn gehat aza hoyf

00:23:41.740 --> 00:23:44.930
me hot nisht gekent araynkumen nor mit aza shlisl, me hot geklungen.

00:23:46.110 --> 00:23:49.039
rukt zikh on dos aynruf tsetl.

00:23:50.193 --> 00:23:52.281
di shvesters hobn es ibergenumen ober

00:23:52.377 --> 00:23:53.780
ikh bin nisht in der heym.

00:23:54.211 --> 00:23:55.814
me hot gezogt ikh bin nisht in der heym.

00:23:59.374 --> 00:24:03.014
se hot zikh ongehoybn a problem vos me zol ton.

00:24:03.100 --> 00:24:04.456
in Satmer iz geven

00:24:04.614 --> 00:24:08.155
a khasidish- zeyer a khasidishe shtot, s'iz dort geven satmere khasidim,

00:24:09.027 --> 00:24:10.689
dey hobn gehat a mineg,

00:24:10.795 --> 00:24:14.175
az tomer me hot bakumen an aynruf tsetl, zey hobn nisht ayngerukt.

00:24:14.344 --> 00:24:16.178
eyner hot zikh gemakht meshuge,

00:24:16.733 --> 00:24:21.006
eyner hot zikh gemakht, eyner hot zikh bahaltn, eyner iz avekgeforn in an andere shtot,

00:24:21.243 --> 00:24:23.041
ober ayngerukt hobn zey nisht.

00:24:25.790 --> 00:24:31.230
bay undz hot zikh demolts oyfgehaltn a yingl fun Karpat, Karpatn Rus,

00:24:31.751 --> 00:24:34.959
er iz geven a shtikl korev, un nokh dem hob ikh gehat, nokh dem der tate hot gehat a COUSIN

00:24:35.089 --> 00:24:38.292
vos er hot shoyn gehat avekgelofn fun Slovakay,

00:24:38.394 --> 00:24:42.654
fun Kashoy keyn Rumenyen, keyn keyn Ungarn, er hot gevolt zikh matsl zayn.

00:24:42.818 --> 00:24:45.647
er fleg oykh araynkumen a sakh mol tsun undz in shtub.

00:24:45.920 --> 00:24:49.740
azoy vi s'iz geven tsvey yinglekh vos ikh hob gevust zenen nisht kosher,

00:24:51.345 --> 00:24:54.250
un ikh aleyn hob oykh nisht gehat keyn groys kheyshek tsu geyn, vayl

00:24:54.349 --> 00:24:57.071
ikh hob gevust kholile me ken mikh aroystrogn keyn Rusnland.

00:24:58.331 --> 00:25:03.372
 der tate iz aroysgegangen zikh zikh barotn mit mit zayne gute brider, vos me zol ton,

00:25:05.135 --> 00:25:07.656
me hot nisht, me hot zikh nisht gekent keyn eytse gebn vos me zol ton.

00:25:07.826 --> 00:25:09.892
endlekh hob ikh bashlosn oyf der nakht,

00:25:10.220 --> 00:25:15.087
ikh ruk ayn. ikh vil nisht shteln in keyn shverikeytn mayne e- m- tatn,

00:25:15.185 --> 00:25:20.126
vos me ken im aroysfirn tsu di politsey, me ken makhn gantse shverikeytn, ikh ruk ayn.

00:25:21.680 --> 00:25:25.782
ikh bin gelofn koyfn a rukzak, mit di ale zakhn,

00:25:25.992 --> 00:25:31.300
shikh, di gantse shikh, mit di ale zakhn vos me broykh hobn tsu aynrukn. mit a koldre.

00:25:33.381 --> 00:25:35.736
ikh hob dem andern in der fri ayngerukt,

00:25:35.765 --> 00:25:40.156
dos iz geven lebn Satmer, draysik kilometer keyn

00:25:41.129 --> 00:25:42.950
SEINI hot es geheysn, SEINI.

00:25:43.089 --> 00:25:45.126
SZINERVARALJA oyf ungarish.

00:25:45.835 --> 00:25:48.031
oyf yidish hot es geheysn Varul.

00:25:49.561 --> 00:25:52.183
ven hot dos pasirt, velkhe...?

00:25:52.212 --> 00:25:54.491
es hot pasirt in yare tsvey un fertsik.

00:25:54.733 --> 00:25:56.041
ende?

00:25:55.912 --> 00:25:58.497
ende tsvey un fertsik, ergets in f-

00:25:59.663 --> 00:26:04.516
AUGUST, in AUGUST ende AUGUST. AUGUST.

