far di yontoyvim?

00:26:06.533 --> 00:26:12.579
dos aynruf tsetl hot geloytet oyf dray khadoshim, oyf nayntsik tog. me zol mitnemen,

00:26:12.709 --> 00:26:16.666
kleyder, oder dos, ales, oyf draysik tog, nokh draysik tog lozt men aheym.

00:26:20.095 --> 00:26:23.051
endlekh, ze'mir dort geven a tsen tsvelef tog,

00:26:23.699 --> 00:26:28.359
mayne shvester zenen mikh aroysgekumen ahin, me hot mir gebrengt zakhn tsu esn, mit andere zakhn,

00:26:29.612 --> 00:26:33.462
mir ho'mir gehoft az me vet undz nisht aroysfirn keyn, funem land, deys iz geven der hoypt...

00:26:34.679 --> 00:26:40.478
der matsev iz geven me zol undz kholile nisht aroysfirn fun land, meyle in land, vet men shoyn zen vos me ken makhn in di medine

00:26:42.084 --> 00:26:48.674
nokh a tsen, tsi nokh tsvelef tog, hot men undz avekgefirt keyn,

00:26:49.916 --> 00:26:51.907
a shtot in di TSHI gegnt,

00:26:51.989 --> 00:26:54.866
SEPSISENTYORG hot es geheysn, an ungarish mokem

00:26:54.928 --> 00:26:58.318
oykh groyse antisemitn geven dort. un shlekhte mentshn,

00:26:58.724 --> 00:27:02.146
vos zey hobn nisht tsugelozt f- fun, undz ze'mir durkhgangen durkh,

00:27:02.845 --> 00:27:07.683
kartofl, vi s'iz geven dos, az mir zol mir aroysnemen kholile a kartofl, men zol undz epes helfn dort, epes, un...

00:27:09.409 --> 00:27:15.577
ze'mir ongekumen ahin hot men undz gezogt mir darf mir makhn farshidene

00:27:15.991 --> 00:27:19.727
griber dort far, kegn di krig, di di SCHUTZGRABEN.

00:27:19.937 --> 00:27:23.058
andere zakhn, mit drotn, mit farshidene SCHUTZ...

00:27:23.753 --> 00:27:27.523
az ven me makht mir fartik di arbet, nokh dem geyn mir aheym.

00:27:27.710 --> 00:27:31.268
vi shnel mir vel mir fartik makhn, mir vel mir fartik makhn di arbet nokh zeks vokhn,

00:27:31.372 --> 00:27:33.001
vel mir aheymgegan nokh zeks vokhn.

00:27:33.820 --> 00:27:35.880
m'iz geganen, me hot oysgeklibn tsvishn undz,

00:27:36.485 --> 00:27:39.404
der tsveyter transport, di arbayts, mayn

00:27:39.705 --> 00:27:46.365
mayn, oylem vos s'iz geven di tsvey hundert mentshn, tsvey hundert tsen mentshn,

00:27:46.844 --> 00:27:51.750
iz geven, ken ikh zogn efsher, zibetsik, finef un zibetsik protsent loyter intelektueln.

00:27:51.928 --> 00:27:56.195
a sakh doktoyrim, a sakh advokatn, inzhenirn,

00:27:57.995 --> 00:28:03.474
s'iz geven yin- mentshn ongehoybn fun tsvontsik yor, biz finef un fertsik, biz akht in fertsik yor. gemisht.

00:28:03.772 --> 00:28:05.101
fun bank direktors.

00:28:08.435 --> 00:28:12.764
s'iz geven eyner nit undz fun NOYBAUM eyner, Vayzer.

00:28:12.879 --> 00:28:17.991
Vayzer Miklosh iz geven der direktor fun der UNK UNK fabrik, a

00:28:18.116 --> 00:28:22.853
khemikaln fabrik, dort hot men gemakht farshidene UNK, toyznter arbayter hobn zey UNK

00:28:22.920 --> 00:28:32.373
tsen toyznter arbayter dort. un...

00:28:32.412 --> 00:28:37.537
me hot oysgeklibn a por mentshn, ver es, ver es zoln zayn, azoy vi in di lager iz geven di kapos, hot men oysgeklibn do

00:28:37.604 --> 00:28:40.650
dey zoln zayn di opakht-gebers, efsher a akht tsen mentshn,

00:28:40.764 --> 00:28:43.437
az di zoln opakht gebn oyf undz,

00:28:43.524 --> 00:28:47.637
s'iz geven a por fakh-layt, a por inzhenirn vos hob ge- farshtanen tsu di arbet,

00:28:48.938 --> 00:28:56.073
yednfals, di mentshn, me hot zikh eynem dem andern geyogt.

00:28:56.430 --> 00:28:57.626
mamesh geyogt,

00:28:58.113 --> 00:29:03.384
se flegn kumen mentshn, heymishe yinglekh fleg ikh UNK UNK, "bist meshuge," zog ikh, "bist narish?"

00:29:03.485 --> 00:29:06.218
"me vet nisht aheymlozn," zog ikh, "nokh, nokh nokh dem.

00:29:06.317 --> 00:29:10.910
me vet trefn andere arbet far undz," zog ikh. un nisht nor ikh bin geven oyf dem meynung, andere zenen oykh geven oyf der meynung.

00:29:11.117 --> 00:29:13.656
s'iz ober dokh geven efsher a dray fir f-

00:29:13.730 --> 00:29:15.614
finef un draysik protsent fun mentshn,

00:29:15.777 --> 00:29:19.193
vos zey hobn gezogt men darf zikh tsuayln mit di arbet vayl me vet geyn aheym.

00:29:20.093 --> 00:29:25.315
yetst veln mir oyfhern di kasete, mir veln aribergeyn oyf di naye kasete.
